---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout
  title="About MyTripTip"
  description="MyTripTip helps first-time travelers plan their Korea trip with practical, decision-focused guides."
>
  <article class="mx-auto max-w-3xl px-4 py-12 prose prose-slate">
    <h1>About MyTripTip</h1>

    <p>
      MyTripTip is a practical travel guide for people visiting Korea for the first time.
      We focus on the decisions that matter most: where to stay, how to get around, which
      tours to book, and what eSIM or transport card to buy.
    </p>

    <h2>What We Do</h2>
    <p>
      Every guide on this site is built around a single decision. We compare options,
      lay out the trade-offs, and give you a clear recommendation so you can book with
      confidence.
    </p>

    <h2>How We Make Money</h2>
    <p>
      Some of our guides include affiliate links to booking platforms like Booking.com,
      Viator, and Airalo. If you book through those links, we may earn a commission at
      no extra cost to you. This is how we keep the site running and our guides free.
    </p>
    <p>
      Affiliate partnerships never influence our recommendations. We recommend what we
      genuinely believe is the best option for first-time visitors.
      See our <a href="/editorial-policy/">Editorial Policy</a> and
      <a href="/affiliate-disclosure/">Affiliate Disclosure</a> for details.
    </p>
  </article>
</BaseLayout>
